Mining Progression
------------------

Mission 1:
	Launch Scanner for a resource
		Ore          :   Stock
		Water        :   MKS
		MetallicOre	 :   MKS
		Minerals     :   MKS
		Substrate    :   MKS
		Kerbinite    :   Kerbinite

	Launch scanner into kerbin orbit
	Land scanner near base1
	


Mission 2:
    Have capacity for mining resource
	Mine for an amount of resource 
		Ore          :   1000
		Water        :   1000
		MetallicOre	 :   1000
		Minerals     :   1000
		Substrate    :   1000
		Kerbinite    :   1000


Mission 3:
	Convert the resource for production
		Liquid Fuel  :  Stock
		Oxidiser     :  Stock
		Other?       :  MKS


Mission 4: 
 	Expand the opperation to multiple resources 
 		Mine for an amount of resource for 3 other types
		Ore          :   1000
		Water        :   1000
		MetallicOre	 :   1000
		Minerals     :   1000
		Substrate    :   1000
		Kerbinite    :   1000 

Mission 5: 
	Use the resources to gain an amount of production materials

Mission 6: Land a launch pad at the base

Mission 7: Build a ship using the resources 